menu "breadboard: bb_thermal"

config BB_THERMAL_AUTOREGISTER
    bool "Auto-register /api/thermal HTTP route via bb_registry"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, bb_thermal self-registers GET /api/thermal through
        bb_registry at order 1 (after order-0 satellites have registered
        their extenders). Disable to call bb_thermal_init manually.
        This is opt-in (default off) to prevent polluting consumers that define
        their own /api/thermal handler or don't have the hardware. Enable this
        config (or call bb_thermal_init) when your app wants BB to own
        the route.

endmenu
